---
// Winter Arc Hook Section
// Timeline graphic with motivational copy
---

<section
  class="py-16 md:py-24 px-4"
  style="background-color: var(--color-rich-earth);"
>
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
    <h2
      class="text-3xl md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-extrabold mb-8 leading-tight"
      style="color: var(--color-jade);"
    >
      66 Days. March 1st. New You.
    </h2>

    <div
      class="mb-16 space-y-6 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed"
      style="color: var(--color-alabaster);"
    >
      <p>
        The science is clear: 66 days to build automatic habits. That's the
        program. That's the commitment. While everyone else wastes winter
        scrolling and making excuses, you're building an unfair advantage.
      </p>
      <p>
        Start now, finish transformed. They'll coast through another season.
        You'll walk into spring, March 1st, as someone completely different.
        Better habits. Higher rating. Actual results.
      </p>
      <p class="font-semibold" style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);">
        This is your winter arc. The gap between you and everyone settling for
        mediocrity starts here. NooLife makes sure you finish what you start.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Timeline Graphic -->
    <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-0 py-8 overflow-x-auto">
      <!-- Start / Day 1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-[3px] z-10"
          style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-sm font-semibold"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Start
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-20 md:w-24 h-[3px] -mt-10"
        style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Week 3 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-[3px] z-10"
          style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-sm font-semibold"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Week 3
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-20 md:w-24 h-[3px] -mt-10"
        style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Week 6 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-[3px] z-10"
          style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-sm font-semibold"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Week 6
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-20 md:w-24 h-[3px] -mt-10"
        style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Week 9 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="w-4 h-4 rounded-full border-[3px] z-10"
          style="background-color: var(--color-faded-khaki); border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-sm font-semibold"
          style="color: var(--color-faded-khaki);"
        >
          Week 9
        </div>
      </div>
      <div
        class="w-20 md:w-24 h-[3px] -mt-10"
        style="background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--color-faded-khaki) 0%, var(--color-jade) 100%);"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Day 66 Complete -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center gap-4">
        <div
          class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full border-[3px] z-10"
          style="background-color: var(--color-jade); border-color: var(--color-mint); box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 208, 156, 0.5);"
        >
        </div>
        <div
          class="text-base md:text-lg font-semibold text-center"
          style="color: var(--color-jade);"
        >
          Day 66<br /><span
            class="font-extrabold text-base"
            style="color: var(--color-mint);">Complete</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
